 hero against your Search Console queries. The gap is wider than you think.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: One quantified outcome appears above the fold" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">008</span>One quantified outcome appears above the fold</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">A real number from a real customer beats every adjective in your thesaurus. If you can&#x27;t source a defensible number, don&#x27;t fake one — a missing number is better than one that won&#x27;t survive a sales call.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-02" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">02</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Headline &amp; Messaging Clarity</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">4<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->9</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The headline passes the 5-second test with non-customers" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">009</span>The headline passes the 5-second test with non-customers</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The cheapest CRO test that exists and almost nobody runs it. Five strangers, five seconds, &#x27;what does this do?&#x27; If three of five can&#x27;t answer, the headline is too clever. &#x27;Clever&#x27; is the most expensive word in landing page copy. It&#x27;s what founders reach for when they&#x27;re bored of their own product. Boring and clear beats clever and ambiguous every time.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The headline sells the outcome, not the mechanism" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">010</span>The headline sells the outcome, not the mechanism</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Close deals faster&#x27; beats &#x27;AI-powered CRM with pipeline analytics.&#x27; The mechanism belongs in section three, where prospects who already care about the outcome go looking for proof. Exception: in developer tools and infra, the mechanism is the outcome. Engineers don&#x27;t trust pages that hide it.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: One page, one promise" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">011</span>One page, one promise</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The most common pattern we see: a homepage selling &#x27;save time&#x27; to operators AND &#x27;grow revenue&#x27; to executives AND &#x27;ship faster&#x27; to engineers. The result converts none of them. Split into separate landing pages by buyer. Route paid traffic to the matching page. The lift from message-match alone usually beats every other change combined.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: The buyer persona is named explicitly in the first screen" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">012</span>The buyer persona is named explicitly in the first screen</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Built for B2B SaaS founders.&#x27; &#x27;Made for product marketers at Series A startups.&#x27; The right visitor feels seen. The wrong one self-disqualifies. The second is undervalued — wrong-fit visitors pollute your funnel metrics and make it harder to learn what&#x27;s working.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: If you target switchers, you name the competitor" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">013</span>If you target switchers, you name the competitor</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;The Notion alternative for engineering teams&#x27; captures someone the moment they land. The visitor has already done half the buying work — they know the category, they know which incumbent they don&#x27;t like, they&#x27;re looking for permission to leave.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Talk to &#x27;you,&#x27; not to &#x27;users&#x27;" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">014</span>Talk to &#x27;you,&#x27; not to &#x27;users&#x27;</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Every &#x27;users can&#x27; becomes &#x27;you can.&#x27; Read your page out loud. The moment you hear yourself describing a product instead of talking to a person, mark it and rewrite.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Every section header is a complete benefit statement, not a label" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">015</span>Every section header is a complete benefit statement, not a label</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Reporting&#x27; is a label. &#x27;See where every dollar of your ad spend went&#x27; is a section header. Most visitors only read your H2s. If a skimmer reading only your H2s couldn&#x27;t reconstruct the offer, your headers are doing decoration work instead of selling work.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: No empty superlatives" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">016</span>No empty superlatives</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Best.&#x27; &#x27;Leading.&#x27; &#x27;World-class.&#x27; &#x27;Next-generation.&#x27; The buyer&#x27;s brain skips every one. Replace each with a fact, a quote, or a number — or delete it. &#x27;Trusted by 8,000 teams&#x27; beats &#x27;the most trusted platform&#x27; because one is checkable and the other is wallpaper.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Reading level at 8th grade or below" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">017</span>Reading level at 8th grade or below</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Even technical buyers skim. The best B2B SaaS pages read like a smart friend explaining the product over coffee. Run Hemingway. Cut anything above grade 9.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-03" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">03</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Social Proof &amp; Trust</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">4<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->7</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Every testimonial has a photo, full name, role, and company" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">018</span>Every testimonial has a photo, full name, role, and company</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;— Marketing Director&#x27; reads as fabricated, because half the time it is. One fully attributed testimonial is worth ten anonymous ones. If you have only one, lead with it. Don&#x27;t dilute it.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: At least one testimonial includes a defensible number" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">019</span>At least one testimonial includes a defensible number</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Saved us 12 hours a week&#x27; beats &#x27;great product, highly recommend&#x27; by an enormous margin. Make it a quarterly habit: ask your three happiest customers for one number they&#x27;d put their name to. You&#x27;ll get at least one.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The logo strip is industry-matched, not impressive-but-random" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">020</span>The logo strip is industry-matched, not impressive-but-random</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">A visitor from the Shopify ecosystem is moved by Shopify-ecosystem logos. They&#x27;re unmoved by your one Fortune 500 client from a totally different vertical. Relevance &gt; fame. Segment the logo strip by referral source if you can — the engineering work is small, the lift is real.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Third-party badges link to live, current pages" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">021</span>Third-party badges link to live, current pages</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">A G2 badge that doesn&#x27;t click through looks Photoshopped. A G2 badge linking to a page where your last review is from 2022 is worse than no badge. Check each one. Sounds trivial. Isn&#x27;t.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Show whatever compliance you have, on or near pricing" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">022</span>Show whatever compliance you have, on or near pricing</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If you serve businesses, name what you&#x27;ve got — even just a &#x27;privacy policy&#x27; link or a &#x27;data hosted in EU&#x27; line near pricing helps. SOC2 and ISO 27001 only matter once you sell to enterprise. Until then, show the smaller wins you do have rather than hiding behind silence — buyers assume the absence is the answer.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Get one video testimonial — even a 30-second phone clip" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">023</span>Get one video testimonial — even a 30-second phone clip</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If you have any happy customer, ask for a 30-second clip recorded on their phone. One scrappy testimonial outperforms zero polished ones. Tone and body language are harder to fake than text, and at indie scale you don&#x27;t need flagship logos — you need proof a real person uses this.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Write up your single best customer story" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">024</span>Write up your single best customer story</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If you have one customer with a real outcome, that&#x27;s enough for one case study at this stage. Problem, solution, result with a number in the headline — and don&#x27;t bury it three clicks deep. One detailed story outperforms five generic testimonials. Don&#x27;t wait until you have ten.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-04" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">04</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Product Demonstration</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">6<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->8</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Annotated screenshots show the real UI" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">025</span>Annotated screenshots show the real UI</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Marketing renders look like aspirations. Annotated screenshots — with arrows, callouts, captions explaining what each piece does — look like proof. Buyers want proof.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: A product video or interactive demo is impossible to miss" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">026</span>A product video or interactive demo is impossible to miss</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Hero or section two. Not button-gated. Not &#x27;scroll down to find it.&#x27; The demo at the bottom of your page is a demo that doesn&#x27;t exist.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The demo video is under 90 seconds" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">027</span>The demo video is under 90 seconds</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Wistia&#x27;s data is consistent: most viewers drop after 60 seconds. The best demos hook in five seconds and deliver the core &#x27;aha&#x27; by 45. If yours is three minutes, cut it in half. If it&#x27;s six, you&#x27;re treating it as documentation, not as a sales tool.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: The &#x27;how it works&#x27; section has three steps, not seven" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">028</span>The &#x27;how it works&#x27; section has three steps, not seven</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Three steps fit in working memory. More steps signal complexity, even when there isn&#x27;t any. If you genuinely can&#x27;t compress to three, the product is more complicated than your buyers want — and that&#x27;s the real problem.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: At least one feature section shows real, populated data" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">029</span>At least one feature section shows real, populated data</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The single most common screenshot mistake we see. &#x27;Project Alpha&#x27; and &#x27;user@example.com&#x27; make the product feel like a demo for a demo. Realistic project names, plausible numbers, real-looking dates make it feel like a working product. Use your own dogfood account if you have to.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Interactive sandbox or no-signup playground is available" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">030</span>Interactive sandbox or no-signup playground is available</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">For any product where signup is a heavy commitment, this is often the single biggest unlock in the entire checklist. Storylane, Arcade, Navattic — all one-day builds. If you&#x27;ve never seriously considered adding one, you&#x27;re probably leaving conversions on the table.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Each feature section opens with the problem, not the feature" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">031</span>Each feature section opens with the problem, not the feature</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Tired of building reports manually every Monday?&#x27; leads. &#x27;Automated reporting dashboard&#x27; follows. Problem-first framing makes the feature feel inevitable. Feature-first leaves the reader asking &#x27;do I need this?&#x27; — which is the wrong question to leave hanging.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Integrations appear as logos, top 6 visible" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">032</span>Integrations appear as logos, top 6 visible</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Works with Slack, HubSpot, Stripe&#x27; removes a major buying objection. Text lists are skipped. Logos are absorbed. If your top integration is also your biggest competitor, lead with it anyway — buyers care more about fit with their stack than your positioning concerns.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-05" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">05</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Pricing Page &amp; Plan Presentation</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">5<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->9</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Pricing is on the page or one click away" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">033</span>Pricing is on the page or one click away</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Contact us for pricing&#x27; works for two kinds of companies: pure enterprise, and brands strong enough that buyers tolerate the friction. If you&#x27;re neither, &#x27;Contact us&#x27; is just SMB buyers reading &#x27;we&#x27;ll figure out how much you can pay&#x27; and leaving. Even ranges work. The fear that publishing prices commoditizes you is almost always smaller than the cost of disqualifying yourself.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Three plans maximum" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">034</span>Three plans maximum</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">More than three columns triggers analysis paralysis. Hide the unusual plans behind a toggle. The pricing page exists to make a choice easy, not to display your full SKU catalog. Founders resist this because they think more plans = more revenue. The opposite is usually true.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The recommended plan is visually highlighted" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">035</span>The recommended plan is visually highlighted</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">A &#x27;Most popular&#x27; badge, a contrasting background, a thicker border. Decision fatigue is real, and most buyers want to be told which plan to pick. Be the guide. Don&#x27;t be coy about which plan you want them on.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Each plan lists 5-7 differentiating features, not 25 checkmarks" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">036</span>Each plan lists 5-7 differentiating features, not 25 checkmarks</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Long lists train the eye to skim and make plans feel interchangeable. Show only what&#x27;s different between plans. The full matrix lives below in a comparison table for the small minority who&#x27;ll actually read it.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Per-seat math is clear and annual savings are shown in dollars" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">037</span>Per-seat math is clear and annual savings are shown in dollars</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Save $X/year&#x27; beats &#x27;-20%&#x27; because the dollar feels real. If invited viewers are free, say so. If everyone is billed, make that obvious. Pricing surprise turns a happy trial into an angry churn faster than anything else.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Every plan has a next step" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">038</span>Every plan has a next step</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The enterprise plan with only &#x27;Contact sales&#x27; loses the buyer who&#x27;s a fit but isn&#x27;t ready to talk. Add &#x27;Or start a free trial&#x27; as a secondary action.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: A &#x27;cancel anytime&#x27; or money-back line sits near pricing CTAs" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">039</span>A &#x27;cancel anytime&#x27; or money-back line sits near pricing CTAs</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Reversibility shrinks decision risk. The buyers who would have abused it were never going to pay long-term anyway. The cost is tiny; the lift is real.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: The pricing page has its own FAQ" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">040</span>The pricing page has its own FAQ</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Pre-answer the five to eight questions buyers ask before paying: refund policy, what happens at the seat limit, what counts as a &#x27;user,&#x27; are there setup fees. Pull from your actual support inbox. If you&#x27;ve answered the same question more than three times this month, it belongs here.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Have a &#x27;Contact us&#x27; option for the rare 10x buyer" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">041</span>Have a &#x27;Contact us&#x27; option for the rare 10x buyer</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Even if 99% of your buyers are self-serve, a &#x27;Contact sales&#x27; option anchors the lower plans as bargains and captures the occasional high-ACV deal that walks in. Don&#x27;t omit it because you&#x27;ve never had one — you&#x27;ll figure out the enterprise product when the first lead arrives.</p></div></div></div></div></di