></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: CTA repeats after every meaningful section (every ~1.5 screens)" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">044</span>CTA repeats after every meaningful section (every ~1.5 screens)</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Most converters click in the bottom half of the page, after they&#x27;ve read the proof. One CTA in the hero is not enough — repeat it after each meaningful section so users never have to scroll back.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Free-trial signup is email-only" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">045</span>Free-trial signup is email-only</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Every additional field drops conversion (HubSpot and Unbounce both have data on this). The signup form is not the place to qualify leads. The signup form is the place to capture them. Qualify in onboarding.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: If you have SSO, make it dominant — if not, skip this" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">046</span>If you have SSO, make it dominant — if not, skip this</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">SSO eliminates typing friction and lifts B2B signup completion meaningfully when it&#x27;s there. But building Google/Microsoft sign-in is a Series A problem, not a micro-SaaS one. If you have it, make it the visually dominant signup option. If you don&#x27;t, ship email + password well first.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: &#x27;No credit card required&#x27; sits next to free-trial CTAs" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">047</span>&#x27;No credit card required&#x27; sits next to free-trial CTAs</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Five-word edit. Consistent lift. If your trial does require a card, ask yourself why. The conversions you lose to that requirement usually outnumber the bad-fit users you screen out.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: If your ACV is over ~$200/mo, offer both demo and self-serve" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">048</span>If your ACV is over ~$200/mo, offer both demo and self-serve</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Enterprise buyers want demos. SMBs want to try it themselves. If your average revenue per customer is north of ~$200/mo, forcing one path leaves money on the table — offer both. Below that, self-serve only is fine and removes a support burden you don&#x27;t need yet.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: What happens after signup is described next to the CTA" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">049</span>What happens after signup is described next to the CTA</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Free for 14 days, then $X/mo. Cancel anytime.&#x27; The visitors most likely to convert are also the most cautious about hidden commitments. Tell them what&#x27;s behind the door before they open it.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-07" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">07</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Lead Capture &amp; Forms</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">3<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->6</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Top-of-funnel forms ask 3 fields or fewer" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">050</span>Top-of-funnel forms ask 3 fields or fewer</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">For &#x27;book a demo&#x27;: email, name, company. Done. Enrich the rest from the email domain or ask on the call. The marketing team&#x27;s desire to qualify at the form is almost always more expensive than the leads it filters out.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: If you take demos, embed Calendly on the page" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">051</span>If you take demos, embed Calendly on the page</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If you do demos at all, embed Calendly or Chili Piper. The &#x27;we&#x27;ll be in touch&#x27; flow is where demo leads die — the friction of waiting for an email, replying, scheduling is enough time for intent to evaporate. If you don&#x27;t do demos yet, skip this.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Lead magnets gate behind email only" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">052</span>Lead magnets gate behind email only</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Phone number on an e-book form is how you get a database full of &#x27;555-555-5555.&#x27; Save deeper qualification for actual buying-intent forms.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Newsletter signup appears on every blog post and in the footer" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">053</span>Newsletter signup appears on every blog post and in the footer</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Capture intent at the moment of value, and again after the user finishes scrolling. Pair with a real reason to subscribe. &#x27;Weekly CRO tips for SaaS founders&#x27; beats &#x27;subscribe to our newsletter&#x27; — the first names what they get, the second names what you want.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The auto-respond welcome email fires within 60 seconds" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">054</span>The auto-respond welcome email fires within 60 seconds</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Trust dies fast. If the promised PDF or trial link isn&#x27;t in their inbox within a minute, they assume it&#x27;s broken and bounce. Test monthly. These things break silently.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Form success states show the next action, not &#x27;Thank you&#x27;" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">055</span>Form success states show the next action, not &#x27;Thank you&#x27;</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The user just signaled high intent. Capitalize on it. &#x27;Check your inbox&#x27; or &#x27;Book your onboarding call&#x27; or &#x27;Watch this 5-minute video&#x27; — anything that keeps momentum beats a digital handshake and a closed door.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-08" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">08</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Objection Handling &amp; FAQ</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">3<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->6</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The FAQ answers uncomfortable questions, not marketing softballs" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">056</span>The FAQ answers uncomfortable questions, not marketing softballs</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Pull from sales calls and support tickets, not from what&#x27;s comfortable to answer. If your FAQ doesn&#x27;t include at least one question that makes your team slightly uncomfortable to answer publicly, it isn&#x27;t doing its job.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: &#x27;How are you different from [Competitor]?&#x27; is answered directly" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">057</span>&#x27;How are you different from [Competitor]?&#x27; is answered directly</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Buyers shortlist three to five vendors. If you don&#x27;t position against the alternatives, they&#x27;ll assume you&#x27;re undifferentiated and pick on price — and you&#x27;ll lose, because someone is always cheaper. Name the competitor. Acknowledge what they&#x27;re good at. Explain when you&#x27;re the better choice. Founders avoid this because it feels aggressive. The avoidance costs more than the awkwardness.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Migration and switching costs are addressed" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">058</span>Migration and switching costs are addressed</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The number one reason buyers stay on inferior tools is switching cost. &#x27;We&#x27;ll import your data from [competitor] in under an hour&#x27; is one of the most powerful sentences you can put on a B2B SaaS page. If you do the migration for them, say so prominently.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Implementation timeline is stated honestly" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">059</span>Implementation timeline is stated honestly</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If yours is fast, brag. If it&#x27;s slow, justify it with what you do during onboarding. The vague answer is always worse than the honest one, even when the honest one is &#x27;this takes time.&#x27;</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Commit to &#x27;export your data anytime&#x27; in writing" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">060</span>Commit to &#x27;export your data anytime&#x27; in writing</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">One sentence on the page — &#x27;export your data anytime in standard formats&#x27; — moves more deals than you&#x27;d expect. Even if the export UI isn&#x27;t built yet, commit to it. Mature B2B buyers look for this, and the absence of the statement is itself a signal.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: If you charge by usage or seats, show one example calculation" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">061</span>If you charge by usage or seats, show one example calculation</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Usage- and seat-based pricing punishes buyers who can&#x27;t model their year-two cost. One worked example (&#x27;a team of 10 at average usage = $X/mo&#x27;) is table stakes for any growth-priced product. Without it, buyers assume the worst and bake the worst into their budget.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-09" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">09</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Page Speed &amp; Core Web Vitals</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">4<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->7</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: LCP under 2.5 seconds on mobile 4G" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">062</span>LCP under 2.5 seconds on mobile 4G</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Users bounce roughly 25% more per extra second (Google&#x27;s published research). LCP is usually the hero. Compress aggressively. Lazy-load everything else. Check your numbers in Search Console, not just locally.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: CLS under 0.1" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">063</span>CLS under 0.1</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Reserve image dimensions. Avoid late-injected banners. Pre-load fonts. Often the easiest CWV to fix and the most overlooked, because developers don&#x27;t notice the jumps on their fast local connections.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: INP under 200ms" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">064</span>INP under 200ms</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Sluggish buttons make your product feel slow before users even sign up. Strip heavy third-party scripts. Defer non-critical JS. Audit your tag manager — half the scripts in there are probably doing nothing useful.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Hero image is WebP or AVIF with responsive srcset" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">065</span>Hero image is WebP or AVIF with responsive srcset</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">A 200KB WebP versus a 1.2MB PNG cuts LCP by half a second on slow connections. Every modern image pipeline supports this. There is no excuse.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Third-party scripts (analytics, chat, A/B) are async or deferred" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">066</span>Third-party scripts (analytics, chat, A/B) are async or deferred</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Synchronous third-party scripts block paint and inflate INP. Audit your tag manager — most things load fine async or after user interaction.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Verify your CDN is actually serving static assets" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">067</span>Verify your CDN is actually serving static assets</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">If you&#x27;re on Vercel, Netlify, or Cloudflare Pages, edge delivery is the default — but custom domains, image hosts pointing at origin, or misconfigured rewrites can quietly bypass it. Check your asset URLs are hitting the CDN, not your origin. If you&#x27;re not on a modern host yet, fix that first; rolling your own CDN is bigger work than it sounds.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Custom fonts use font-display: swap and are preloaded" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">068</span>Custom fonts use font-display: swap and are preloaded</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">FOIT (flash of invisible text) hurts perceived speed and CLS. font-display: swap and &lt;link rel=preload&gt; together eliminate the worst font-loading regressions.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-10" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">10</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Mobile Experience</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">4<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->5</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Hero text is readable without zooming (16px+ body, 28px+ H1)" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">069</span>Hero text is readable without zooming (16px+ body, 28px+ H1)</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Tiny mobile type makes users pinch-zoom or bounce. 16px body is the absolute floor — 18px is better for B2B audiences over 35 (which is most of them).</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Primary CTA is full-width or near-full-width on mobile" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">070</span>Primary CTA is full-width or near-full-width on mobile</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Thumb-reach matters. A full-width button is the easiest tap target and signals &#x27;the next step&#x27; louder than a centered button surrounded by air. Both improve mobile conversion.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Mobile nav collapses to a hamburger that contains the CTA" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">071</span>Mobile nav collapses to a hamburger that contains the CTA</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Don&#x27;t hide signup three taps deep. Many users open the menu specifically looking for it. Keep the CTA visible in the mobile header too, if space allows.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Embedded video uses a lightweight poster, not autoplaying MP4" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">072</span>Embedded video uses a lightweight poster, not autoplaying MP4</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Mobile data, battery, and tab freezing kill mobile autoplay. Poster image, play overlay, load video only on tap. Saves the visit, the conversion, and your CWV scores simultaneously.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: Pricing stacks vertically on mobile" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">073</span>Pricing stacks vertically on mobile</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Horizontal-scroll pricing on mobile is unusable. One vertical card per plan, recommended plan first. Check it on a real phone, not by resizing your browser window — half your traffic might be seeing a broken page right now.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-white overflow-hidden" style="border:1.5px solid #0b0b0c;border-radius:14px"><div class="px-3 sm:px-5 py-5"><div id="section-11" class="scroll-mt-32"><div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-3 mb-4 px-1"><span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold tabular-nums transition-colors duration-300 bg-[#0b0b0c]" style="width:44px;height:44px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;transform:skew(-4deg);box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #ff3b1f"><span style="transform:skew(4deg)">11</span></span><div class="flex-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5 sm:pt-0"><h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#0b0b0c] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);letter-spacing:-0.02em">Onboarding &amp; Activation Hooks</h2></div><div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0 pt-1 sm:pt-0"><span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold px-2 py-1 bg-white text-[#ff3b1f] border-[1.5px] border-[#ff3b1f] uppercase tracking-wider tabular-nums" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="display:inline-block;transform:skew(4deg)">2<!-- --> high-impact left</span></span><span class="text-sm font-bold tabular-nums text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace">0<!-- -->/<!-- -->6</span></div></div><div class="h-[3px] bg-[#e6e3dc] rounded-full mb-2 overflow-hidden mx-1"><div class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-300 bg-[#ff3b1f]" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mt-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: The signup confirmation links straight into the product" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">074</span>The signup confirmation links straight into the product</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x27;Check your email to verify&#x27; is where activations go to die. Every second the user spends switching apps is a second they might decide not to come back. Magic links, SSO, auto-login. Verify in the background.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#ff3b1f]/35 border-l-[#ff3b1f] bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.05)] hover:bg-[rgba(255,59,31,0.08)] hover:border-[#ff3b1f]/60"><button aria-label="Check: First-run guides the user to one specific &#x27;aha&#x27; in under 5 minutes" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#ff3b1f]/40 hover:text-[#ff3b1f]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-bold text-[#0b0b0c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#ff3b1f]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">075</span>First-run guides the user to one specific &#x27;aha&#x27; in under 5 minutes</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><span class="inline-flex items-center text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 bg-[#ff3b1f] text-white" style="transform:skew(-4deg)"><span style="transform:skew(4deg);display:inline-block">High Impact</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Pick the single behavior most correlated with retention. Walk users there. Don&#x27;t show them everything the product can do — show them the one thing that makes them say &#x27;oh, I get it.&#x27; Everything else waits until session two.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: The welcome email and the in-app tour push the same next action" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">076</span>The welcome email and the in-app tour push the same next action</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">The most common new-user paralysis happens when the email says &#x27;do X first&#x27; and the tour says &#x27;do Y first.&#x27; Two &#x27;do this firsts&#x27; equals zero. Pick one path. Reinforce it from both channels.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: The in-app tour highlights 1-3 features, not every screen" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">077</span>The in-app tour highlights 1-3 features, not every screen</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Long tours train users to click &#x27;Skip&#x27; forever — and on every product they ever use afterward, so you&#x27;re damaging the entire SaaS ecosystem one bad tour at a time. The best tours are under 60 seconds.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: Empty states tell first-time users exactly what to do" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">078</span>Empty states tell first-time users exactly what to do</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">An empty dashboard with &#x27;Import sample data&#x27; beats an empty dashboard with a generic help link. Empty states are the first product surface most users see. Treat them as onboarding copy, not as design afterthoughts.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl border-[1.5px] transition-all duration-150 border-l-[3px] pl-[15px] border-[#d4d0c5] border-l-[#0b0b0c] bg-white hover:bg-[#fafaf7] hover:border-[#0b0b0c]/40"><button aria-label="Check: A sample workspace or pre-populated demo is available" class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 focus:outline-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle w-[22px] h-[22px] transition-colors text-[#c9c5bb] hover:text-[#6b6b70]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></button><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="w-full text-left focus:outline-none group/title"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="flex-1 font-medium text-[#1a1a1c] text-[15px]" style="letter-spacing:-0.01em"><span class="mr-2 inline-block tabular-nums text-[11px] font-bold align-[1px] text-[#0b0b0c]" style="font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em" aria-hidden="true">079</span>A sample workspace or pre-populated demo is available</span><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 text-[#c9c5bb] group-hover/title:text-[#6b6b70] transition-all duration-200" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></button><p class="text-[15px] text-[#2a2a2d] leading-[1.55] pr-4 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 max-h-0 opacity-0" aria-hidden="true">Letting users see the product populated removes the &#x27;I have to do work before I see value&#x27; friction that kills activation. Often the difference between a 20% activation rate and a 60% one.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main><footer class="print:hidden" style="padding:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--ls-line);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:var(--font-jetbrains-mono), monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ls-mute);letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;background:var(--ls-paper);max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto"><div>© 2026 PageGains · J2FB SAS</div><div style="display:flex;gap:24px"><a class="hover:opacity-100 opacity-60 transition-opacity" href="/blog">Blog</a><a class="hover:opacity-100 opacity-60 transition-opacity" href="/free-resources">Free Resources</a><a class="hover:opacity-100 opacity-60 transition-opacity" href="/legal">Legal</a><a href="mailto:info@pagegains.com" class="hover:opacity-100 opacity-60 transition-opacity">Contact</a></div></footer></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"PageGains","url":"","logo":"/gainbot-icon.png"}</script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script></body></html>